%Scale the output
%%scale 1.0
%%format dulcimer.fmt
X:1
T:
C:
M:    %(3/4, 4/4, 6/8)
L:    %(1/8, 1/4)
V:1 clef=treble
K:    %(D, C)

If you don't want a repeat bracket on voice 2, add:

V:2
%%repbra 0

after K:.

Otherwise, if you want a normal repeat bracket, remove the bar between
the staves by:

%%score 1 2
